When writting file, please follow the python file structure best practice 

├── app/
│   ├── __init__.py         # marks as package
│   ├── main.py             # main entry point (Streamlit/FastAPI/etc.)
│   ├── config.py           # app configs, env settings
│   ├── models.py           # AI models, LLM wrappers, etc.
│   ├── memory.py           # memory or session management
│   ├── ui.py               # frontend (Streamlit, NiceGUI, Gradio components)
│   └── utils.py            # helper functions, small utilities